Licencing Information for OLA
=========================================

C++
-----------------------------------------
The files required for libola and libolacommon are licenced under the LGPL,
this means you are free to link against the OLA client library in your own
programs.

The files required for libolaserver and olad are licenced under the GPL.

Python
------------------------------------------
The Python client API is LGPL, the examples and RDM Responder Test Suite is
GPL.

